Hot as hell. That's Shione Cooper, July 2010 SCORE covergirl, in this fresh video hot off the camera. Shione has been a girl of mystery since she debuted. She does flammable, nut-busting sex scenes but few knew any personal details about the doll-faced brunette from the Czech Republic since she rarely gives interviews. In the opener of Hot As Hell, Shione speaks to the SCORE Studio manager about her background and her interests before sex-date Kamil shows up to go to fucktown with this buxom beauty. As it turns out, Shione is more shy than anyone realized, although you'd never know it seeing her get wild on camera. Or guess that Shione used to be a punky, Gothy girl with short, dyed hair before first becoming a glamour model and then more recently a hardcore bad girl. Her sweetness really comes out during the early segment of this video. So there's really two Shiones here, the good bad girl and the bad good girl! And that's a good thing! Thank you, Shione Cooper.
